<section id="digital-solutions">
##  🌱 Digital Solutions for Farmers

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i></span> Mobile Apps for Farmers
- <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></span> **Market Price Alerts** — Real-time commodity pricing to guide selling decisions.
- <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-cloud-sun"></i></span> **Weather Forecasts** — Hyperlocal predictions to optimize planting and harvesting.
- <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-virus"></i></span> **Crop Disease Detection** — AI-powered image recognition for early intervention.

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></span> Farmer Data Platforms
- <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-seedling"></i></span> **Farm Productivity Tracking** — Monitor yields, inputs, and seasonal trends.
- <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd"></i></span> **Access to Financial Services** — Connect with microfinance and insurance providers.
- <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></span> **Community Knowledge Sharing** — Share best practices and success stories across networks.
</section>

---

<section id="geospatial-intelligence">
## 🗺️ Geospatial Intelligence

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i></span> Land & Resource Optimization
- Soil health mapping using satellite and drone data.
- Flood/drought risk detection for climate resilience.
- Land suitability modeling for crop rotation and expansion.
</section>

---

<section id="supply-chain">
## 🚚 Supply Chain & Market Linkage

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-truck"></i></span> AI-Powered Logistics
- Predict harvest windows and optimize transport routes.
- Forecast urban demand to reduce market gluts.
- Smart aggregation centers with sensor-based inventory tracking.
</section>

---

<section id="cooperative-intelligence">
## 🧠 Cooperative Intelligence

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i></span> Empowering Farmer Groups
- AI-driven credit scoring for SACCOs and cooperatives.
- Group-based yield prediction for collective bargaining.
- Behavioral nudges via SMS/WhatsApp for timely action.
</section>

---

<section id="livestock-aquaculture">
## 🐄 Livestock & Aquaculture

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-fish"></i></span> Smart Monitoring
- Image/audio recognition for livestock disease detection.
- IoT sensors for water quality and fish growth in aquaculture.
</section>

---

<section id="research-extension">
## 🧪 Research & Extension Support

### <span class="fa-icon"><i class="fas fa-flask"></i></span> Data-Driven Innovation
- Train AI models on local crop disease datasets.
- Digitize indigenous knowledge using NLP.
- Adaptive trials to evaluate interventions across zones.
</section>

